Quickstrike:





"Aw, dang it!" Quickstrike realized that he was alone. He bolted to the 
vent, and attemtped to jump up into the shaft, but it was too high up. He 
tried two more times, but with no avail.

"Beast mode." He transformed to beast mode and climbed up the wall, into the 
shaft. He crawled though it. "Dark Mouse. Dark Mouse. Hey rodent, where ya 
at?"
